    "title": "Mid-Level Investment Banker at Paytm Money Capital India",
    "description": "Grow your career with Paytm Money Capital India! We are hiring a Investment Banker for our Pune team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Paytm Money Capital India:\nPaytm Money Capital India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Paytm Money Capital India!",
